    <string name="about_text">
        <p>PomoTodo is an application that helps you do your homework in time intervals called PomoTodos.</p>
        <p>Between each interval or PomoTodo, rest periods are defined to improve your concentration.</p>
        <p>The tasks are obtained from the task management service called Toodledo (http://www.toodledo.com).</p>
        <p>I hope you find it useful.</p>
